{
  "id": "69ace1735177935891fb809a",
  "title": "井戸端のダークテーマを無効化する方法",
  "created": 1772937589,
  "updated": 1772998816,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69ace1735177935891fb809a",
      "text": "井戸端のダークテーマを無効化する方法",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772938243
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace40100000000005bf454",
      "text": "を検討する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772938243,
      "updated": 1772938243
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d5385",
      "text": "from [井戸端にダークテーマを導入したい]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d5386",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d5387",
      "text": "井戸端をダークテーマで閲覧しない人はどうすべきか",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d5388",
      "text": " 端末の[ダークモード]がオンの時、[箇条書きのバレットをFontAwesomeにするUserCSS]の配色などの変数がダークテーマ仕様になってしまう",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937705
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d5389",
      "text": "\t案1. 端末のダークモードをオフにする",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d538a",
      "text": "\t\t他のアプリの配色も明るくなる",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d538b",
      "text": "\t案2. CSS変数を参照するコンテナクエリーを使ってそれ用のUserCSSを生やす",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d538c",
      "text": "\t\t欠点はパフォーマンス面の問題があること",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d538d",
      "text": "\t\t同じ変数を二箇所に設置するのは避けたい",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d538e",
      "text": "\t\t\tまあ標準テーマの値は滅多に変わるものではないが‥",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d538f",
      "text": "\t\tcode:example.css",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d5390",
      "text": "\t\t\t:root {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d5391",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t--is-dark: false;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d5392",
      "text": "\t\t\t}",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d5393",
      "text": "\t\t\t@media screen and (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d5394",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t:root {\t--is-dark: true;\t}",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d5395",
      "text": "\t\t\t}",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d5396",
      "text": "\t\t\t@container (--is-dark: false) {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d5397",
      "text": "\t\t\t\thtml {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d5398",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t/* ライトテーマの変数の値を複製する (--page-bg 等) */",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d5399",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t}",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d539a",
      "text": "\t\t\t}",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d539b",
      "text": "\t\tcode:turn-off-dark-theme.css",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d539c",
      "text": "\t\t html {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d539d",
      "text": "\t\t \t--is-dark: false;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d539e",
      "text": "\t\t }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d539f",
      "text": "\t副作用少なく解除できる方法があればすばらしいが…[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d53a0",
      "text": "\t でも元々[ScrapboxのTheme]はメンバー全員強制だから、それと比べれば各々が変えられる方法があるだけ良しか",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d53a1",
      "text": "\t [/customize/Auto Dark Themes] の逆のUserCSSを作成するのが最も良い方法かもしれない[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d53a2",
      "text": "\t案3. `(prefers-color-scheme: dark)`時にライトテーマの変数で上書きするUserCSSを作成する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d53a3",
      "text": " \t\t[Auto Dark Themes] の逆パターン",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d53a4",
      "text": "\t\t各自でUserCSSに`@import url('') (prefers-color-scheme: dark);`を書けばよくなる",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d53a5",
      "text": "\t\t同じ変数を2箇所に設置しなければならないのは案2.と同じ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772938175
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d53a7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772937589
    },
    {
      "id": "69ace17200000000009d53a8",
      "text": "そもそも、端末/ブラウザの設定がダークなのに井戸端をダークで見たくないという人がいるのか[wogikaze.icon]",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1772937589,
      "updated": 1772998816
    },
    {
      "id": "69add0890000000000f76fdd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1772998795,
      "updated": 1772998795
    }
  ]
}